(86, 'DJ1', 'Private Tour of Plitvice Lakes', 3, NULL, 7, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Experience the world-famous Plitvice Lakes on this private guided walking tour. Your professional guide will take you to explore this huge national park with its 16 lakes and countless waterfalls in this spectacular UNESCO Site. You can decide whether you want to visit the Lower Lakes, Upper Lakes or both. You?ll be mesmerised by falls like Veliki Prstavac, Mali Prstavac and the ?Great Waterfall,? along with countless other smaller cascades, and the surreal hues of the lakes which range in colour from aquamarine to brilliant emerald. At the end of the tour you can hop on the train for a panoramic ride back to the north-side entrance.', 'Private guided tour including tickets. Add 30 ? per additional pax     Meeting Point - Hotel Lobby', 'Comfortable clothing, walking  footwear, sunglasses, sunscreen and water', NULL, NULL),
